channels.description:
Celebration Radio broadcasts and streams encouraging contemporary Christian music and features programming that focus on Biblical values and provides practical help in dealing with the challenging issues of life.   
Celebration Radio is funded by direct contributions from those who listen to KAMB and choose to provide financial support. We are deeply grateful for our listeners who recognize the spiritual value of KAMB's ministry and understand the need to help support it.  You can donate today at https://dsnp.co/GOfV4D.  
KAMB is licensed to serve the city of Merced, CA and can be heard on the following FM frequencies:
101.5FM Merced-Modesto-Fresno; 
103.1FM Santa Cruz; 
100.9FM South San Jose; 
96.3FM Salinas/Monterey area; 
107.1FM Sonora area.
